node.text:
WATCH THIS: At my dad’s last birthday, we had t-shirts made of him! Now think about how meta this is: My dad is in this photo. And in this photo, my dad is wearing a shirt of a photo where my dad was in that photo. This feels like the start of a Rick and Morty episode. Throw some Mr. Nimbus in there and I’m watching. 

P.S. Have you ever thought about Passive Income? My team and I are looking for a few more ppl who want to earn a full-time passive income from home using AirBNB without owning property. If you’re interested, message me the word “Travel”. Thanks!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jason Capital on September 04, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people standing, indoor and text that says 'C Capital Jason'.

node.text:
What’s your dog’s name? This is Sterling in front of 800 people at the High-Status Summit 2019. I wanted to make it like Lion King and give Sterling his “Simba” moment. I may have even told him “Sterling, everything the light touches is yours”. 😂 Sterling’s got a great home but not all dogs do. I see homeless dogs in Puerto Rico and it kills me. My team and I just started to run promos every month to raise money for Hope For Paws (they rescue dogs facing death or danger through abuse or abandonment). Dogs are our “furry little homeys” - I will always have dogs and always take the best care of them I can. 

P.S. Do you like Instagram? My team and I are looking for a few more ppl who want to earn a full-time income from home just typing messages on social media. If you’re interested, message me the word “Mentor”. Thanks!
